title: Kylie Minogue - Greatest Hits 87-98 [2004] DVD5
description: Kylie Minogue - Greatest Hits 87-98 [2004] DVD5 Kylie Ann Minogue OBE (born 28 May 1968) is an Australian-British singer and actress. signed to record label PWL in 1987 and released her first studio album Kylie the next year. She is recognised as the highest-selling Australian artist of all time by the Australian Recording Industry Association (ARIA). Greatest Hits: 87–99 is a 2003 compilation album by Australian singer Kylie Minogue. The album was a budget release, released only in Australia during the same month as Minogue's ninth studio album Body Language. The accompanying DVD (titled Greatest Hits 87–98) features every Minogue music video released during the PWL and Deconstruction years (the only Minogue DVD to do so).
